      • simpleMethodCallExample

        public long simpleMethodCallExample(long sleepTime)
                             throws Exception
        A simple wrapper method that will expose a call joinpoint on a Profiled method. If the AbstractTimingAspect isn't correctly configured, this will result in a log line in addition to the line generated by the execution of the simpleTest method.
        Throws:
        Exception
